&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Mesh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Mesh, our mission is to enable consumers to pay and be paid with any asset. Today, trillions of dollars in tokenized assets exist but remain largely unusable for everyday commerce. Mesh is bridging this gap by making crypto payments reliable, useful, and ubiquitous. We combine a powerful orchestration engine with a seamless consumer app to unlock liquidity for the world. Backed by leading investors like PayPal Ventures, Paradigm, and Galaxy Ventures, we are building the infrastructure for the next era of the global economy. Join us!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Mesh, we&#39;re building an AI-first company where intelligence is embedded into how we operate, build, and scale. We&#39;re looking for an AI Enablement Lead to help drive that transformation by identifying the company&#39;s biggest operational bottlenecks, building AI-powered solutions that eliminate friction, and creating systems that unlock leverage across every team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a highly cross-functional role at the intersection of Product, Engineering, GTM, and Operations. You&#39;ll partner directly with company leaders to solve high-impact business challenges, deploy AI workflows and automations that teams rely on every day, and help redefine how work gets done at Mesh. Beyond building solutions, you&#39;ll establish the playbooks, standards, and internal AI infrastructure that enable the entire organization to move faster, operate smarter, and scale more efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify high-impact opportunities where AI can eliminate manual work, accelerate execution, and unlock outsized business value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with executives and functional leaders to solve critical operational challenges across the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and launch AI-powered workflows, automations, copilots, and internal tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own initiatives end to end, from opportunity discovery and prioritization to implementation, adoption, and measurement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive company-wide AI adoption through enablement, training, and hands-on partnership with teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish repeatable frameworks, playbooks, and best practices that empower teams to leverage AI effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure and communicate business impact, tying initiatives to efficiency gains, productivity improvements, and adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build the foundation of Mesh&#39;s AI operating system, including the tools, standards, and infrastructure that will shape how the company operates for years to come&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
