&lt;li&gt;Lead renewals and expansion negotiations, including pricing, contract terms, and deal structure, in partnership with Sales and CS leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run weekly or bi-weekly check-ins and monthly and quarterly business reviews, tracking performance, surfacing risks early, and aligning on success metrics&lt;/li&gt;
