&lt;li&gt;Represent the voice of strategic customers internally, balancing customer needs with company priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to meet customers, strengthen relationships, and represent Mesh at key industry event&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
