&lt;li&gt;Build and present solution designs that map Mesh&#39;s APIs, SDKs, and smart routing capabilities to customer use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical input on deal scoping, including feasibility and integration complexity estimates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted technical advisor throughout the sales cycle, building confidence with customer engineering and product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide customer engineering teams through SDK and API integration, from sandbox to production launch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the technical implementation process for APAC accounts, coordinating with US-based Solutions Architects on complex builds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct integration reviews and troubleshoot issues during onboarding to reduce time-to-live&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain region-specific playbooks, implementation guides, and best practices documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track implementation milestones and proactively communicate status to internal stakeholders and customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive adoption and optimization post-launch, helping customers scale volume and expand use cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the first point of technical triage for APAC customer issues during regional business hours&lt;/li&gt;
